Package org.eclipse.pde.build

Pluggable repository support for eclipse.fetch.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Constants Constants for the files usually manipulated by the fetch factory.
IAntScript Interface providing helper methods to produce Ant scripts.
IFetchFactory Interface to be implemented by clients of the org.eclipse.pde.build.fetchFactories extension-point.
 

Package org.eclipse.pde.build Description

Pluggable repository support for eclipse.fetch.

Package Specification

This package contains the interfaces necessary to contribute a new repository support to the eclipse.fetch task of PDE Build.
